{"tid":1121642,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友今日做檢查","createTime":"2019-04-23T12:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T16:53:24.000Z","uid":65433,"like":210,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8909ab156fb9900e2821f40bcb2685d4ed2ef244","tid":1121642,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:36:12.000Z","msg":"呢排做嘢大壓力到仆街，為咗份糧又唔敢quit，聽日放完長假要返工(攞埋今日假)，我尋日已經唔開心定，夜晚發惡夢，今朝成朝都好down，覺得人生好灰。<br />\n<br />\n女朋友三年前割咗瘤，最近嗰度有啲乸住乸住，驚咗成個月，排期今日檢查。<br />\n下午佢打嚟...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n...話醫生check完話無事<br />\n<br />\n我一聽到，忽然間個人開朗咗<br />\n覺得為咗能夠令佢有更好更舒服嘅生活，辛苦啲無所謂<br />\n又有返力量面對聽日嘅挑戰<br />\n<br />\n我呢一刻發現原來佢開心比我開心更加重要<br />\n<br />\n搵到一個相愛嘅人過人世，原來真係可以令個世界無咁殘酷<br />\n<br />\n只要有佢同我一齊，我一定可以survive到呢個人生低谷<br />\n<br />\n希望所有人都能夠得到呢份幸福"},{"pid":"5773c73d19495052a88c42217cbcf994479cd056","tid":1121642,"uid":159697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:38:49.000Z","msg":"加油 自己比心機搵多d"},{"pid":"bdc8d297167c18d98e4f65a10f7b2db5414a61c9","tid":1121642,"uid":69302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:44:26.000Z","msg":"加油 努力"},{"pid":"ac09adca23958734270190a078d12dab3147beec","tid":1121642,"uid":114449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:51:06.000Z","msg":"好羨慕你女朋友"},{"pid":"1d7702dceb6a439d9e7667ad494bb2a599d25e69","tid":1121642,"uid":118945,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6e34c21966b1fb4475071b2c692138f080ad36","tid":1121642,"uid":121060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b993c70a72dff459895bafcca218a5b34a43229","tid":1121642,"uid":98049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:58:33.000Z","msg":"加油，祝福你哋"},{"pid":"513fe8247df1986c1066cb9c876a